</script></div><div class="tz-hero-content__text-container"><h1 class="tz-h1 tz-hero__title"><span aria-label="School of Engineering &amp; Technology">School of Engineering<br> &amp; <mark style="color:#42a5f5">Tech</mark>nology</span></h1></div></div></div></section><!-- hero end--><!-- about us start--><section class="tz-about-section"><div class="tz-container tz-about__root" style="--tz-about-bg-accent-color:#42a5f5"><svg class="tz-about-bg-el-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 220.415 200.259" width="220.415" height="200.259" aria-hidden="true" data-ignore="true"><defs><linearGradient id="tz-about-bg-gradient" x1="48.59" y1="188.76" x2="195.72" y2="27.47" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse" gradientTransform="translate(.836 .316)"><stop offset=".43" stop-opacity=".3" style="stop-color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--tz-about-bg-accent-color)40%,white 60%)"></stop><stop offset=".99" style="stop-color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--tz-about-bg-accent-color)50%,white 50%)"></stop></linearGradient></defs><path fill="url(#tz-about-bg-gradient)" d="M205.926 0.315h-85.2c18.81 13 31.14 34.7 31.14 59.29 0 39.79-32.25 72.04-72.04 72.04-15.28 0-29.43-4.77-41.09-12.88l-37.9 55.61c22.45 15.48 49.66 24.56 78.99 24.56 76.94 0 139.32-62.38 139.32-139.32 0-21.21-4.75-41.3-13.22-59.29v-.01Z"></path></svg><img class="tz-about-bg-el-2" src="/assets/admissions/background-elements/about-bg-element-2.25_02_2025.webp" alt="Circular background element" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" decoding="async" width="300" height="550"><div class="tz-about__inner-root"><div class="tz-about__header-wrapper"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-about__header-title" data-aos="fade-up"><span aria-label="About engineering and technology at IIMT University">About<br>Engineering<br>&amp; Technology<br>at IIMT University</span></h2></div><div class="tz-about__list-wrapper"><ul class="tz-about__list" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ItemList" style="--tz-about-list-item-border-color:#42a5f5"><li class="tz-about__list-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="1"><h3 class="tz-about__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Diverse <br>Program Offerings!</h3><p class="tz-about__list-item-description" itemprop="description">From Diploma to Masters, SET provides a variety of programs catering to different engineering disciplines.</p></li><li class="tz-about__list-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="2"><h3 class="tz-about__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Industry-Aligned<br> Curriculum!</h3><p class="tz-about__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Courses are designed under the supervision of industry experts and experienced academicians, regularly updated to meet current industry standards.</p></li><li class="tz-about__list-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="3"><h3 class="tz-about__list-item-title" itemprop="name">State-of-the-Art<br>Laboratories!</h3><p class="tz-about__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Equipped with modern facilities, providing hands-on experience to students.</p></li><li class="tz-about__list-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="4"><h3 class="tz-about__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Holistic<br>Development!</h3><p class="tz-about__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Focus on both theoretical knowledge and practical skills, preparing students for real-world challenges.</p></li><li class="tz-about__list-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="5"><h3 class="tz-about__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Experienced<br>Faculty!</h3><p class="tz-about__list-item-description" itemprop="description">A team of dedicated and knowledgeable faculty members committed to student success.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></section><!-- about us end--><!-- programs start--><section class="tz-scrollspy tz-programs-section" id="programs" style="--tz-programs-header-border-color:#42a5f5"><div class="tz-container tz-programs__root"><div class="tz-programs__inner_root"><div class="tz-programs__header-wrapper"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-programs__header_title" data-aos="fade-up">UG Programs</h2><div class="tz-programs__list-wrapper"><ul class="tz-programs__list" role="list" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/EducationalOccupationalProgram" style="--tz-program-content-card-bg:#42a5f5"><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/bachelor-of-technology-civil-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of B.Tech in Civil Engineering (CE)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Undergraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">B.Tech in Civil Engineering (CE)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A four-year undergraduate program aiming to produce quality civil engineers.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for B.Tech in Civil Engineering (CE)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/bachelor-of-technology-electrical-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of B.Tech in Electrical and Electronics Engineering (EEE)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Undergraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">B.Tech in Electrical and Electronics Engineering (EEE)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A four-year undergraduate program designed under the supervision of industry experts in electrical engineering.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for B.Tech in Electrical and Electronics Engineering (EEE)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/bachelor-of-technology-mechanical-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of B.Tech in Mechanical Engineering (ME)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Undergraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">B.Tech in Mechanical Engineering (ME)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A four-year professional undergraduate program dealing with mechanical engineering principles.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for B.Tech in Mechanical Engineering (ME)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/bachelor-of-technology-computer-science-and-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of B.Tech in Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Undergraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">B.Tech in Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A four-year undergraduate program in computer science and engineering, focusing on the latest technological advancements.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for B.Tech in Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/bachelor-of-technology-artificial-intelligence-and-machine-learning.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of B.Tech in Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning (AI &amp; ML)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Undergraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">B.Tech in Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning (AI &amp; ML)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A four-year undergraduate program specializing in artificial intelligence and machine learning within computer science and engineering.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for B.Tech in Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning (AI &amp; ML)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="tz-programs__inner_root"><div class="tz-programs__header-wrapper"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-programs__header_title" data-aos="fade-up">PG Programs</h2></div><div class="tz-programs__list-wrapper"><ul class="tz-programs__list" role="list" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/EducationalOccupationalProgram" style="--tz-program-content-card-bg:#42a5f5"><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-computer-science-and-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A postgraduate program designed for students to pursue advanced careers in computer science and engineering.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-construction-technology-and-management.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Construction Technology &amp; Management (CTM)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Construction Technology &amp; Management (CTM)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">An interdisciplinary postgraduate program focusing on building planning, project coordination, and enhancing knowledge and skills.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Construction Technology &amp; Management (CTM)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-environmental-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Environmental Engineering" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Environmental Engineering</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A postgraduate program concerned with tasks related to biodiversity, wasteland management, and environmental balance.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Environmental Engineering" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-power-electronic-and-drives.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Power Electronics &amp; Drives (PED)" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Power Electronics &amp; Drives (PED)</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A postgraduate program offering opportunities to delve into power electronics and drives, with potential for entrepreneurship.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Power Electronics &amp; Drives (PED)" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-structural-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Structural Engineering" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Structural Engineering</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A postgraduate program aiming to produce quality engineers in the field of structural engineering.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Structural Engineering" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-transportation-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Transportation Engineering" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Transportation Engineering</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">An interdisciplinary postgraduate program focusing on various aspects of transportation engineering.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Transportation Engineering" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li><li class="tz-programs__list-item" role="listitem" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-programs__content_card_image-wrapper"><picture><img class="tz-programs__content_card_image" src="/assets/admissions/school-of-engineering-and-technology/programs/master-of-technology-production-engineering.27_02_2025.webp" alt="Image of M.Tech in Production Engineering" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" itemprop="image" width="471" height="871" decoding="async"></picture></figure><div class="tz-programs__content_card_text"><p class="tz-programs__content_card_chip">Postgraduate</p><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-programs__content_card_title" itemprop="name">M.Tech in Production Engineering</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-programs__content_card_description" itemprop="description">A postgraduate program in the Department of Mechanical Engineering, specializing in production engineering.</p><a class="tz-programs__apply-button" aria-label="Apply now for M.Tech in Production Engineering" itemprop="potentialAction" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ApplyAction" href="#apply-now-form"><span class="tz-programs__apply-button_label" itemprop="name">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-programs__apply-button_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></li></ul></div></div></div></section><!-- programs end--><!-- career opportunities start--><section class="tz-scrollspy tz-career-opportunities-section" id="career-opportunities" aria-labelledby="career-opportunities-heading" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ItemList" style="--tz-career-opportunities-accent-color:#42a5f5"><div class="tz-container tz-career-opportunities__root"><div class="tz-career-opportunities__inner-root"><div class="tz-career-opportunities__header-wrapper" data-aos="fade-up"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-career-opportunities__header_title" id="career-opportunities-heading">Career Opportunities</h2></div><ul class="tz-grid tz-career-opportunities__list"><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="1"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Software Developer"><span>Software Developer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Design, develop, and maintain software applications for various industries.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="2"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Data Scientist"><span>Data Scientist</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Analyze complex data sets to extract insights and develop predictive models.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="3"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="AI/ML Engineer"><span>AI/ML Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Build and deploy machine learning models to solve real-world problems.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="4"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Cybersecurity Analyst"><span>Cybersecurity Analyst</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Protect systems and networks from cyber threats and vulnerabilities.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="5"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Cloud Engineer"><span>Cloud Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Design and manage cloud computing infrastructure for businesses.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="6"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Web/App Developer"><span>Web/App Developer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Develop and optimize websites and mobile applications for user engagement.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="7"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Full Stack Developer"><span>Full Stack Developer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Work on both frontend and backend development to create complete web applications.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="8"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Machine Learning Researcher"><span>Machine Learning Researcher</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Conduct research on advanced machine learning algorithms and applications.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="9"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Data Engineer"><span>Data Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Design and maintain data pipelines to support analytical applications.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="10"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Automation Specialist"><span>Automation Specialist</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Implement automation solutions to improve efficiency in industrial processes.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="11"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Design Engineer"><span>Design Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Create and develop innovative designs for mechanical systems and products.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="12"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Manufacturing Engineer"><span>Manufacturing Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Optimize production processes to enhance efficiency and quality.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="13"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Quality Control Engineer"><span>Quality Control Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Ensure product quality and compliance with industry standards.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="14"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Automotive Engineer"><span>Automotive Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Develop and improve automotive systems, engines, and designs.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="15"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Structural Engineer"><span>Structural Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Design and analyze buildings and infrastructure for stability and safety.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="16"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Construction Project Manager"><span>Construction Project Manager</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Oversee construction projects from planning to execution.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="17"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Site Engineer"><span>Site Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Supervise on-site construction activities and ensure compliance with regulations.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="18"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Urban Planner"><span>Urban Planner</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Develop plans for city infrastructure and sustainable urban growth.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="19"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Electrical Design Engineer"><span>Electrical Design Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Design electrical systems for buildings, machinery, and power distribution.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="20"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Power Systems Engineer"><span>Power Systems Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Work on power generation, distribution, and optimization projects.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="21"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Renewable Energy Specialist"><span>Renewable Energy Specialist</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Develop sustainable energy solutions like solar and wind power.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="22"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Embedded Systems Engineer"><span>Embedded Systems Engineer</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Design and develop embedded systems for smart devices and automation.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="23"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Government Sector Jobs"><span>Government Sector Jobs</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Opportunities in PSUs like BHEL, NTPC, ONGC, DRDO, ISRO, Indian Railways, and IES.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="24"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Defense Services"><span>Defense Services</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Join the Indian Army, Navy, or Air Force in technical roles.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="25"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Private Sector &amp; MNC Jobs"><span>Private Sector &amp; MNC Jobs</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Work with top companies like TCS, Infosys, Wipro, HCL, ibm.25_02_2025, Microsoft, L&amp;T, and Google.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="26"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Entrepreneurship &amp; Startups"><span>Entrepreneurship &amp; Startups</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Start your own business in AI, automation, construction, and renewable energy.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="27"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Higher Studies &amp; Research"><span>Higher Studies &amp; Research</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Pursue M.Tech, MBA, MS abroad, or Ph.D. for advanced knowledge and research.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="28"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Blockchain &amp; Cybersecurity"><span>Blockchain &amp; Cybersecurity</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Develop secure digital solutions in the growing blockchain and cybersecurity domain.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="29"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Internet of Things (IoT)"><span>Internet of Things (IoT)</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Work on connected smart devices for automation and efficiency.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="30"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Smart Cities &amp; Sustainable Energy"><span>Smart Cities &amp; Sustainable Energy</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Contribute to the development of sustainable urban infrastructure.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="31"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Robotics &amp; Automation"><span>Robotics &amp; Automation</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Develop intelligent robots for industrial and commercial applications.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-career-opportunities__list-item" itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="32"><h3 class="tz-h5 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-title" itemprop="name" aria-label="Big Data &amp; Cloud Computing"><span>Big Data &amp; Cloud Computing</span></h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-career-opportunities__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Handle large-scale data processing and cloud-based solutions for businesses.</p></li></ul></div></div></section><!-- career opportunities end--><!-- why choose start--><section class="tz-scrollspy tz-why-choose-section" id="why-choose" aria-labelledby="why-choose-heading" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ItemList"><div class="tz-container tz-why-choose__root"><div class="tz-why-choose__inner-root"><div class="tz-why-choose__header"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-why-choose__header-title" id="why-choose-heading" itemprop="name" data-aos="fade-up"><span aria-label="Why Choose Bachelor of Technology (B.Tech) course?">Why Choose Bachelor of<br> <mark style="color:#42a5f5">Tech</mark>nology Course?</span></h2></div><div class="tz-why-choose__list-wrapper"><ul class="tz-grid tz-why-choose__list" role="list" itemprop="itemListElement" style="--tz-why-choose-list-item-border-color:#42a5f5"> <li class="tz-grid-item tz-why_choose__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" itemprop="itemListElement" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="1"><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-why-choose__list-item-title" itemprop="name">High Demand &amp;<br>Career Opportunities</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-why-choose__list-item-description" itemprop="description">B.Tech graduates are highly sought after in industries such as IT, manufacturing, construction, electronics, and AI, offering diverse career paths.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-why_choose__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" itemprop="itemListElement" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="2"><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-why-choose__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Problem-Solving &amp;<br> Innovation</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-why-choose__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Engineering programs develop analytical thinking and problem-solving skills, making graduates capable of designing solutions for real-world challenges.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-why_choose__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" itemprop="itemListElement" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="3"><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-why-choose__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Technological Advancements &amp;<br> Future Scope</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-why-choose__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Fields like Artificial Intelligence, Data Science, Robotics, and Automation are booming, and a B.Tech degree ensures adaptability to these emerging technologies.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-why_choose__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" itemprop="itemListElement" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="4"><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-why-choose__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Strong Earning Potential</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-why-choose__list-item-description" itemprop="description">Engineering is among the highest-paying career fields, with lucrative job offers from top tech companies and multinational corporations.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-why_choose__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" itemprop="itemListElement" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="5"><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-why-choose__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Global Recognition &amp; Higher Education Pathways</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-why-choose__list-item-description" itemprop="description">A B.Tech degree is globally recognized and serves as a foundation for further studies like M.Tech, MBA, or specialized certifications.</p></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-why_choose__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" itemprop="itemListElement" data-aos="fade-up"><meta itemprop="position" content="6"><h3 class="tz-h3 tz-why-choose__list-item-title" itemprop="name">Entrepreneurship &amp; Startups</h3><p class="tz-body1 tz-why-choose__list-item-description" itemprop="description">With technical knowledge and industry insights, B.Tech graduates can launch startups or work on innovative projects in various engineering fields.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></section><!-- why choose end--><!-- recruiters start--><section class="tz-scrollspy tz-recruiters-section" id="recruiters"><div class="tz-container tz-recruiters__root"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-recruiters__heading" data-aos="fade-up">Our Recruiters and Associates</h2><ul class="tz-grid tz-recruiters__list" role="list"><li class="tz-grid-item tz-recruiters__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-recruiters__list-item-figure"><picture><img class="tz-recruiters__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/recruiters/dlf.25_02_2025.webp" alt="Logo DLF" itemprop="logo" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="137" height="140" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-sr-only" itemprop="name">DLF</figcaption></figure></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-recruiters__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-recruiters__list-item-figure"><picture><img class="tz-recruiters__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/recruiters/romsons.25_02_2025.webp" alt="Logo Romsons" itemprop="logo" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="137" height="140" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-sr-only" itemprop="name">Romsons</figcaption></figure></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-recruiters__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization" data-aos="fade-up"><figure class="tz-recruiters__list-item-figure"><picture><img class="tz-recruiters__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/recruiters/abb.25_02_2025.webp" alt="Logo ABB" itemprop="logo" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="137" height="140" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-sr-only" itemprop="name">ABB</figcaption></figure></li><li class="tz-grid-item tz-recruiters__list-item" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype