lass="swiper-slide tz-rankings__swiper-slide" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem"><meta itemprop="position"><div itemprop="item" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/CollegeOrUniversity"><figure class="tz-rankings__list-item-figure"><picture><source srcset="/assets/admissions/rankings/green-campus.24_03_2025@1743w.avif 1743w, /assets/admissions/rankings/green-campus.24_03_2025@1443w.avif 1443w, /assets/admissions/rankings/green-campus.24_03_2025@1143w.avif 1143w, /assets/admissions/rankings/green-campus.24_03_2025@843w.avif 843w" type="image/avif"><img class="tz-rankings__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/rankings/green-campus.24_03_2025.webp" alt="Image of Green Rankings 2024 by R. World Institutional Ranking" itemprop="image" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="300" height="300" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-h6 tz-rankings__list-item-caption"> <span class="tz-ranking-description" itemprop="description">Green Rankings 2024 - Gold Band - given by R. World Institutional Ranking</span></figcaption></figure></div></div><div class="swiper-slide tz-rankings__swiper-slide" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem"><meta itemprop="position"><div itemprop="item" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/CollegeOrUniversity"><figure class="tz-rankings__list-item-figure"><picture><img class="tz-rankings__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/rankings/best-colleges-of-india.20_03_2025.webp" alt="Image of Top 50 Best Private Institutions" itemprop="image" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="300" height="300" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-h6 tz-rankings__list-item-caption"> <span class="tz-ranking-description" itemprop="description">Top 50 Best Private Institutions in 2024 - given by India Today</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="tz-scrollspy tz-events-section" id="events" aria-labelledby="tz-events-heading" style="--tz-event-accent-color:#42a5f5"><div class="tz-container tz-events__root"><div class="tz-grid tz-events__inner-root"><div class="tz-grid-item tz-events__header-wrapper"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-events__heading" id="tz-events-heading" data-aos="fade-up">Events and Media</h2><div class="tz-events__description-wrapper"><p class="tz-body1 tz-events__description" data-aos="fade-up">Stay up-to-date with the latest events and media coverage from the IIMT University.</p></div></div><div class="tz-grid-item tz-events__list-wrapper"><!-- Swiper container--><div class="swiper tz-events__swiper-container"><div class="swiper-wrapper" role="list"><div class="swiper-slide" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Event"><figure class="tz-events__list-item-figure" data-aos="fade-up"><picture><img class="tz-events__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/events/resumeology.27_05_2025.webp" alt="Your Resume creates your First Professional Picture and to make it simply the best; join us on the Day 3 of The Training Talk" itemprop="image" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="300" height="300" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-body2 tz-events__list-item-caption" itemprop="name">Your Resume creates your First Professional Picture and to make it simply the best; join us on the Day 3 of The Training Talk</figcaption></figure></div><div class="swiper-slide" role="listitem" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Event"><figure class="tz-events__list-item-figure" data-aos="fade-up"><picture><img class="tz-events__list-item-image" src="/assets/admissions/events/ksa-session.27_05_2025.webp" alt="Essential ingredients that determine one's Personality &amp; Professionalism are KSA (Knowledge, Skills and Attitude)" itemprop="image" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="low" width="300" height="300" decoding="async"></picture><figcaption class="tz-body2 tz-events__list-item-caption" itemprop="name">Essential ingredients that determine one's Personality &amp; Professionalism are KSA (Knowledge, Skills and Attitude)</figcaption></figure></div></div><!-- Swiper navigation buttons--><button class="swiper-button-prev" aria-label="Previous event"></button><button class="swiper-button-next" aria-label="Next event"></button></div></div></div></div></section><!-- faq start--><section class="tz-scrollspy tz-faq-section" id="faq" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage"><div class="tz-container tz-faq__root"><div class="tz-faq__inner-root"><div class="tz-faq__header"><h2 class="tz-h2 tz-faq__title" data-aos="fade-up">Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div><div class="tz-accordion tz-faq__accordion" id="tz-faq-accordion"><div class="tz-accordion-item tz-faq__accordion-item" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-aos="fade-up"><button class="tz-h5 tz-accordion__header tz-faq__accordion__header" tabindex="0" id="accordion-s7dpqj2fr-header" aria-label="Toggle What undergraduate engineering programs does IIMT University offer?" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-s7dpqj2fr-content" itemprop="name"><span>What undergraduate engineering programs does IIMT University offer?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button><div class="tz-body1 tz-accordion__content tz-faq__accordion__content" id="accordion-s7dpqj2fr-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-s7dpqj2fr-header" aria-hidden="true" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop="text"><p>IIMT University offers the following Bachelor of Technology (B.Tech) programs: </p><ul> <li>Computer Science Engineering</li> <li>Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning</li> <li>Civil Engineering</li> <li>Electrical Engineering</li> <li>Mechanical Engineering</li> </ul> <p></p></div></div></div><div class="tz-accordion-item tz-faq__accordion-item" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-aos="fade-up"><button class="tz-h5 tz-accordion__header tz-faq__accordion__header" tabindex="0" id="accordion-fddme7sz1-header" aria-label="Toggle What postgraduate engineering programs are available at IIMT University?" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-fddme7sz1-content" itemprop="name"><span>What postgraduate engineering programs are available at IIMT University?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button><div class="tz-body1 tz-accordion__content tz-faq__accordion__content" id="accordion-fddme7sz1-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-fddme7sz1-header" aria-hidden="true" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop="text"><p>The university offers several Master of Technology (M.Tech) programs, including: </p><ul> <li>Computer Science Engineering</li> <li>Construction Technology &amp; Management</li> <li>Electronics &amp; Communication Engineering</li> <li>Environmental Engineering</li> <li>Power Electronics &amp; Drives</li> <li>Production Engineering</li> <li>Structural Engineering</li> <li>Transportation Engineering</li> </ul> <p></p></div></div></div><div class="tz-accordion-item tz-faq__accordion-item" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-aos="fade-up"><button class="tz-h5 tz-accordion__header tz-faq__accordion__header" tabindex="0" id="accordion-t6uyye6ws-header" aria-label="Toggle Are there diploma programs in engineering offered by IIMT University?" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-t6uyye6ws-content" itemprop="name"><span>Are there diploma programs in engineering offered by IIMT University?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button><div class="tz-body1 tz-accordion__content tz-faq__accordion__content" id="accordion-t6uyye6ws-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-t6uyye6ws-header" aria-hidden="true" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop="text"><p>Yes, IIMT University offers diploma programs in engineering, such as: </p><ul> <li>Diploma in Civil Engineering</li> <li>Diploma in Computer Science Engineering</li> <li>Diploma in Electrical Engineering</li> <li>Diploma in Mechanical (Automobile) Engineering</li> </ul><p></p></div></div></div><div class="tz-accordion-item tz-faq__accordion-item" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-aos="fade-up"><button class="tz-h5 tz-accordion__header tz-faq__accordion__header" tabindex="0" id="accordion-dl06jlhlh-header" aria-label="Toggle What is the placement support provided by the university?" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-dl06jlhlh-content" itemprop="name"><span>What is the placement support provided by the university?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button><div class="tz-body1 tz-accordion__content tz-faq__accordion__content" id="accordion-dl06jlhlh-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-dl06jlhlh-header" aria-hidden="true" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop="text"><p>The university has a dedicated placement cell that provides training, internships, and job opportunities with reputed companies.</p></div></div></div><div class="tz-accordion-item tz-faq__accordion-item" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-aos="fade-up"><button class="tz-h5 tz-accordion__header tz-faq__accordion__header" tabindex="0" id="accordion-emgkar43k-header" aria-label="Toggle How can I apply for admission?" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-emgkar43k-content" itemprop="name"><span>How can I apply for admission?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button><div class="tz-body1 tz-accordion__content tz-faq__accordion__content" id="accordion-emgkar43k-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-emgkar43k-header" aria-hidden="true" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop="text"><p>You can apply online through the official website or visit the university campus for offline registration.</p></div></div></div><div class="tz-accordion-item tz-faq__accordion-item" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-aos="fade-up"><button class="tz-h5 tz-accordion__header tz-faq__accordion__header" tabindex="0" id="accordion-hoi2ae3f7-header" aria-label="Toggle Whom can I contact for more details?" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-hoi2ae3f7-content" itemprop="name"><span>Whom can I contact for more details?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button><div class="tz-body1 tz-accordion__content tz-faq__accordion__content" id="accordion-hoi2ae3f7-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-hoi2ae3f7-header" aria-hidden="true" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop="text"><p>You can contact the university's admission helpline or visit the campus for further assistance.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><!-- faq end--></main><footer class="tz-footer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization" role="contentinfo" style="--tz-footer-accent-color:#42a5f5"><div class="tz-footer__root"><div class="tz-footer__inner-root"><div class="tz-container tz-footer__top-bar-wrapper"><div class="tz-grid tz-footer__top-bar"><p class="tz-grid-item tz-footer__title tz-h3"> Unlock endless opportunities &amp; shape your future with <span itemprop="name">IIMT University</span></p><div class="tz-grid-item tz-footer__actions"><a class="tz-footer__apply-now" href="#apply-now-form" aria-label="Apply Now"><span class="tz-body1 tz-footer__apply-now_label">Apply Now</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right tz-footer__apply-now_icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></div></div></div><div class="tz-container tz-footer__connect-with-us__root"><div class="tz-footer__connect-with-us__inner-root"><div class="tz-footer__connect-with-us__address" itemprop="address" ite